title: Soulja Boy Explains Suicidal Snapchat Drama: “People Tend To Think Celebrities Don’t Have Feelings”
text: Soulja Boy Saturday, 17 October 2015 (20 minutes ago) Atlanta rapper Soulja Boy has stepped up to provide more context behind penning a suicidal-esque message on his Snapchat account this week. Despite apologizing earlier this week, SB further explained his message and blamed stress for fueling his lapse in judgement. “Yeah, I’m good, man, I just think, like, being a person in my shoes […] The post Soulja Boy Explains Suicidal Snapchat Drama: “People Tend To Think Celebrities Don’t Have Feelings” appeared first on For The Best In Hip-Hop News - SOHH.com.
